FBIS4-41710 "drsov124_d_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-124 Daily Report 26 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Defense Ministry Owes Pacific Fleet R70 Billion Defense Ministry Owes Pacific Fleet R70 Billion LD2606203994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 2000 GMT 26 Jun 94 LD2606203994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] The debt of the Russian Defense Ministry to the Pacific Fleet since the beginning of the year amounts to around 70 billion rubles. This was revealed at a meeting between State Duma Chairman Ivan Rybkin, who is leading a parliamentary delegation on a tour of Siberia and the Far East, and the Command of the Fleet in Petropavlovsk-Kamchatskiy. Apart from financial problems, the meeting also focused on the problems of manning the armed forces and scrapping stocks of ammunition.
